Thèmes de recherche et d'intérêt / Research topics

   Profil : Probabilités (processus stochastiques) et statistiques
   appliquées
     * Stochastic models for large interacting systems, in particular for
       physics and life sciences ; complex systems
     * Random fields, Gibbs measures, spin systems, interacting particle
       systems, probabilistic cellular automata (PCA)
     * Mathematical and probabilistic aspects on statistical mechanics
     * Applied probability, stochastic algorithms, MCMC methods,
       stochastic simulations and modelling
     * Applied statistics to life sciences, clustering, data statistical
       analysis, text mining
     * Statistical computing, R programming

